Get 45% off the Magic Mind bundle with with my link: [https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN](https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN)  Spider-Man has faced some amazing foes on the big screen, but which baddies are truly spectacular and which ones are just... meh? In this episode of the Major Issues Podcast, we’re bringing back Tier Factor, our totally scientific and not-at-all biased ranking system, to stack up every live-action Spider-Man villain from Goblin-glorious to Rhino-ridiculous.

Will Willem Dafoe’s Green Goblin finish it at the top? Does Topher Grace’s Venom even stand a chance? And where do we put whatever The Amazing Spider-Man 2 was doing? Join us as we web-sling through the best and worst of Spidey’s rogues, laugh at some questionable CGI choices, and probably argue way too much about Jamie Foxx’s Electro.

Suit up, because with great rankings comes great responsibility! 🎙🕷️🔥

